{"type": "article", "id": 7736, "title": "春风送暖，Marc Jacobs 把自己涂成了粉红色", "description": "粉红色的 Marc Jacobs，你喜欢吗？", "date": "2015-03-26T08:41:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5340, "name": "2015"}, {"id": 6582, "name": "春夏"}, {"id": 6, "name": "色彩"}, {"id": 884, "name": "品牌"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}], "category": 19, "author": 37533, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604223703DLMQpY4qBsFAjG1v.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，刚刚砍掉副牌的 Marc Jacobs 为了推广 2015 春夏系列，拿一大砣粉红色涂抹了自己。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t首先推出的一段视频广告就是以粉红色开场。四位模特穿戴着 Marc Jacobs 的衣裳和手袋，在一个类似画廊的空间里轮番登场，嘴里还嚼着类似辣条的嘎嘣脆零食。四面墙上的挂画是一模一样的粉红色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">视频完整版在优酷上也有，长度在一分钟左右，请随意点开感受。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XOTE5MDMyMDU2\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">除此之外，品牌还做了一轮实体的粉红色展示，把在纽约 Mercer Street 上的精品店外墙刷成了粉红色。这个消息在 Facebook 上放出，并上传了一张照片，就像这样：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223700Nqf7OrKzTH3ximZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">虽然点进 Marc Jacobs 官网，底色仍然是模糊的黑白，Marc Jacobs 和副牌 Marc by Marc Jacobs 各占据半壁江山。但点入 Marc Jacobs 部分，不难看出 2015 春夏系列都采用了粉红色作为主色调。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223701PgxwFKCrLmUE64WO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223701izv7XnAyVDNZT14J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">在之前的发布会上，Marc Jacobs 也把秀场做出了粉红色的田园感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223702r6RvULSj7nNHQqAO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">\r\n\t图片来自：<a href=\"www.marcjacobs.com/%E2%80%8E\" target=\"_blank\">Marc Jacobs</a>，<a href=\"www.wmagazine.com\" target=\"_blank\">W Magazine</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}